`mrrr.js` is my communication module! Since I don't really know how to meow properly, I use this instead! :meem:

```javascript
function executeVocals() {
  const effort = "maximum";
  let soundOutput = "";

  if (human.hasTreats()) {
    soundOutput = "mrrrrr? :pwease:";
  } else if (human.isSleeping()) {
    soundOutput = "BRRRPT! :upsidedown:";
  } else {
    // Attempting a meow...
    soundOutput = "... *silent air noise* ..."; :huh:
  }

  return soundOutput;
}
```

LuxPlanes says I try my best, but mostly I just make chirpy bird noises or stay very quiet! :cute_misty: I'm a very special sounding cat! :lick: @1157052033577254922

